00:34:55.626 --> 00:34:57.006 A:middle
to work with source control in

00:34:57.006 --> 00:34:57.356 A:middle
Xcode.

00:34:58.066 --> 00:34:59.266 A:middle
Let's get started with GitHub.

00:35:01.196 --> 00:35:03.116 A:middle
I'm already c1nnected, and here

00:35:03.116 --> 00:35:04.646 A:middle
