know exactly where I want those

00:58:54.426 --> 00:58:57.326 A:middle
layers to be, or I can just drag

00:58:57.326 --> 00:58:58.716 A:middle
them right into my layer stack.

00:58:59.326 --> 00:59:02.316 A:middle
That's pretty awesome, right?

00:59:02.316 --> 00:59:03.556 A:middle
I never get tired of seeing that

00:59:03.556 --> 00:59:04.046 A:middle
happen.

00:59:05.516 --> 00:59:09.936 A:middle
[ Applause ]

